<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Glocal Prayer Network</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo img {
      max-width: 200px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #4a4a4a;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="logo">
    <img src="https://glocalprayer.net/prayer/public/assets/img/glocal-prayer-logo.png" alt="Glocal Prayer Network Logo" />
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h1>Welcome to Glocal Prayer Network</h1>

    <p>Dear <%= data.org_name %>,</p>

    <p>We are delighted to welcome you onboard the Glocal Prayer Network. Our vision is to see people come into a closer relationship with God through prayer and supplication.</p>

    <p>We're pleased to inform you that your organization has been verified by Glocal Prayer Network. You can now access our platform using your credentials.</p>

    <h2>Getting Started</h2>
    <p>To begin your journey with us, please use the following options to log in:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Web Access:</strong> <a href="https://glocalprayer.net/prayer/login">https://glocalprayer.net/prayer/login</a></li>
      <li><strong>Mobile App:</strong> Download our <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.glocalprayer.ep&pcampaignid=web_share">Glocal Prayer app</a> from the Google Play Store</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="https://glocalprayer.net/prayer/login" class="button">Log In Now</a>

    <h2>Team Registration</h2>
    <p>Please share the following link with your team members for registration:</p>
    <p><a href="https://glocalprayer.net/prayer/appuserregistration/<%= data.short_code %>">https://glocalprayer.net/prayer/appuserregistration/<%= data.short_code %></a></p>

    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at admin@glocalprayer.net</p>

    <p>Thank you for joining us in our mission. We look forward to praying together!</p>

    <p>Blessings,<br>The Glocal Prayer Network Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
